top_new/MPU2/Home_0__container__" style="border: 0pt;"><iframe id="google_ads_iframe_/1024780/Desktop_new/MPU2/Home_0" name="google_ads_iframe_/1024780/Desktop_new/MPU2/Home_0" title="3rd party ad content" width="300" height="250" scrolling="no" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" frameborder="0" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: 300px; height: 250px;" aria-label="Advertisement" tabindex="0" data-google-container-id="4" data-load-complete="true"></iframe></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="bg-white p-4"><h2 class="text-cbThmClrLgt text-base font-extrabold undefined">SPECIALS</h2><div class="flex flex-col gap-5 pt-2"><div><a href="/cricket-news/137515/in-a-city-shaped-by-textbooks-abhigyan-kundu-chose-the-bat"><div class="relative"><img alt="in-a-city-shaped-by-textbooks-abhigyan-kundu-chose-the-bat" loading="lazy" width="290" height="160" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-md" style="color: transparent; width: 100%; height: auto;" srcset="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/i1/c841776/in-a-city-shaped-by-textbooks-abhigyan-kundu-chose-the-bat.jpg?d=low&amp;p=det 1x, https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/i1/c841776/in-a-city-shaped-by-textbooks-abhigyan-kundu-chose-the-bat.jpg?d=high&amp;p=det 2x" src="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/i1/c841776/in-a-city-shaped-by-textbooks-abhigyan-kundu-chose-the-bat.jpg?d=high&amp;p=det"></div><div class="text-cbDarkShadGrey pt-1 hover:underline text-base font-bold">In a city shaped by textbooks, Abhigyan Kundu chose the bat</div></a><div class="text-cbTextGrayDark">In Navi Mumbai, where academic security often trumped sporting ambition, Abhigyan Kundu's rise is the story of a coach's faith, a family's trust and a young cricketer's single-minded commitment to his craft</div></div><div><a href="/cricket-news/137503/coffee-chaos-and-clarity-24-minutes-with-sarah-taylor"><div class="relative"><img alt="coffee-chaos-and-clarity-24-minutes-with-sarah-taylor" loading="lazy" width="290" height="16